text: Jorge Rosado (12 January 1939 - 9 June 2009) was a Mexican wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle flyweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Mexican male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mexico Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City Category:Pan American Games medalists in wrestling Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Mexico Category:Wrestlers at the 1959 Pan American Games Category:Wrestlers at the 1963 Pan American Games
